    "COSMIN requires multiple group factor analysis or DIF analysis to be used to assess cross-cultural validity 71.",
    "Reliability.",
    "Reliability refers to the proportion of total variance in the measurement which is because of true differences among participants.",
    "COSMIN requires reliability to be assessed by intra-class correlation coefficients or weighted Kappa and it requires multiple observations in time 71.",
    "Measurement error."
  ]
